    XMLGenerator

    public class ListGenerator<X>
extends java.lang.Object
implements XMLGenerator
    Class to turn Collection into a HTML list. There is a static method to perform one-off formatting. or an object instance can be wrapped round the collection to create a XMLGenerator A ContentBuilder will be able to add a collection directly via ContentBuilder#addList(Collection)
